{"name":"Future Sight (Su)","permission":{"default":0,"KvztsnF1yG9WE5bC":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 9th level, once each day, the astrologian may declare that an action&nbsp;<span lang=\"en-US\">she</span>&nbsp;has just taken did not happen.&nbsp;<span lang=\"en-US\">She</span>&nbsp;may then take a different action.&nbsp;<span lang=\"en-US\">She</span>&nbsp;can do this after the results of&nbsp;<span lang=\"en-US\">he</span>r action are known. The mixing of future and present is disorienting.&nbsp;<span lang=\"en-US\">She</span>&nbsp;is shaken for 1d4 rounds after&nbsp;<span lang=\"en-US\">she</span>&nbsp;uses this ability. This does not stack with other fear effects, but nothing can remove this condition. At 12th level, and every&nbsp;<span lang=\"en-US\">three astrologian</span>&nbsp;levels thereafter,&nbsp;<span lang=\"en-US\">she</span>&nbsp;can use this ability an additional time per day.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Support"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"free"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":"Previous Action"},"range":{"value":null,"units":"personal","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":"none"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"day","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1","maxFormula":"floor((@classes.astrologian.lvl - 6)/3)"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formulaicAttacks":{"count":{"formula":"","value":null},"bonus":{"formula":""},"label":null},"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":"","damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":"0","type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"User is Shaken for [[1d4]] rounds.","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":[],"dictionary":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Astrologian"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"nonlethal":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","disabled":false},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"0DDsamlS9BAmqKMZ"}
{"_id":"0pvUD9CLzhQ7Oa9A","name":"Astrology Secrets: Guiding Star (Su)","permission":{"default":0,"KvztsnF1yG9WE5bC":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/astrologian/astrology-secrets/\">Astrology Secrets</a></p>\n<p>Guiding Star (Su)<span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span></p>\n<p>Whenever the astrologian can see the open sky at night, she can determine her precise location. When the night sky is visible to the astrologian, she may also add her Charisma modifier to her Wisdom modifier on all Wisdom-based checks. In addition, once per night while outdoors, she can cast one spell as if it were modified by the Empower Spell, Extend Spell, Silent Spell, or Still Spell feat without increasing the spell&rsquo;s MP cost or level.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Metamagic"],["Astrology Secret"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"standard"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":""},"uses":{"value":1,"max":1,"per":"day","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1","maxFormula":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formulaicAttacks":{"count":{"formula":"","value":null},"bonus":{"formula":""},"label":null},"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[{"_id":"hq5q5x76","formula":"@abilities.cha.mod","operator":"add","target":"","subTarget":"wisSkills","modifier":"enh","priority":0,"value":0},{"_id":"talsie4l","formula":"@abilities.cha.mod","operator":"add","target":"","subTarget":"will","modifier":"enh","priority":0,"value":0},{"_id":"n6pzimll","formula":"@abilities.cha.mod","operator":"add","target":"","subTarget":"wisChecks","modifier":"enh","priority":0,"value":0}],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":[],"dictionary":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Astrologian"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"nonlethal":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"conditionals":[],"identifiedName":"Astrology Secrets: Guiding Star (Su)"},"flags":{},"effects":[]}
{"name":"The Heavenly Paths (Su)","permission":{"default":0,"KvztsnF1yG9WE5bC":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 5th level, early on in astrologian&rsquo;s studies, she learns about two different sects that map the stars using the positions of the sun and the moon and these two sects are reflective of their reference points. The Diurnal Sect uses the sun as their reference point, creating star maps with the sun being the key to navigation, while the Nocturnal Sect uses the moon as the reference point. The astrologian imbues herself with a specific sect and draws the powers from them. The astrologian may switch between sects as a swift action.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Diurnal Sect (Su):&nbsp;The astrologian is able to empower her healing spells with the power of the sun. When she casts a spell that restores the hit points of an ally, she may leave a regenerative effect. After the spell is cast, allies affected gain Fast Healing equal to the spell&rsquo;s level for a number of rounds equal to the astrologian&rsquo;s Wisdom modifier. Multiple healing spells do not stack, but refreshes the duration.</li>\n<li>Nocturnal Sect (Su):&nbsp;The astrologian is able to empower her healing spells with the power of the moon. When she casts a spell that restores the hit points of an ally, she may leave a shielding effect. After the spell is cast, allies affected gain Damage Reduction/- equal to the spell&rsquo;s level for a number of rounds equal to the astrologian&rsquo;s Wisdom modifier. Multiple healing spells do not stack, but refreshes the duration.</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Stance"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"swift"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":"Self"},"range":{"value":null,"units":"personal","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":"personal"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formulaicAttacks":{"count":{"formula":"","value":null},"bonus":{"formula":""},"label":null},"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":[],"dictionary":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Astrologian"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"nonlethal":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","disabled":false},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"17Ux0m1zXVrk7UtT"}
{"name":"Do-Over (Su)","permission":{"default":0,"KvztsnF1yG9WE5bC":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><span lang=\"en-US\">At&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"en-US\">7</span><span lang=\"en-US\">th level, the astrologian</span>&nbsp;may immediately reroll a failed skill check, saving throw or attack roll.&nbsp;<span lang=\"en-US\">She</span>&nbsp;must accept the second roll regardless of its value.&nbsp;<span lang=\"en-US\">She</span>&nbsp;can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 +&nbsp;<span lang=\"en-US\">he</span>r Wisdom modifier.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Rolls"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"immediate"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":"Previous Attack roll, Skill Check, or Saving throw"},"range":{"value":null,"units":"personal","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":"none"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"day","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1","maxFormula":"@classes.astrologian.lvl+3"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formulaicAttacks":{"count":{"formula":"","value":null},"bonus":{"formula":""},"label":null},"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":[],"dictionary":[]},"featType":"classFeat","asso