{"name":"Sect Powers: Solar Wind (Su)","permission":{"default":0,"KvztsnF1yG9WE5bC":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/astrologian/sect-powers/\">Sect Powers</a></p>\n<p>Solar Wind (Su)</p>\n<p>At 8th level, while under the Diurnal Sect, the astrologian can unleash a blast of searing wind at a single target within 30 feet as a ranged touch attack with no range increment. The solar wind deals 1d6 points of fire damage + 1 for every 2 astrologian levels she possesses. At 11th level, she can also knock an opponent back, treating the blast as a bull rush combat maneuver that uses her caster level + her Wisdom modifier in place of her CMB.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Sect Power"],["Diurnal"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"standard"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":"30","units":"ft","maxIncrements":"1","minValue":null,"minUnits":"melee"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"Solar Wind!","actionType":"rsak","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[["1d6+floor(@classes.astrologian.lvl/2)","Fire"]],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formulaicAttacks":{"count":{"formula":"","value":null},"bonus":{"formula":""},"label":""},"formula":"","ability":{"attack":"dex","damage":"","damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":"0","type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"At 11th level, this attack comes with a bull rush of +[[@classes.astrologian.lvl+@abilities.wis.mod]].","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":[],"dictionary":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Astrologian"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"nonlethal":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","disabled":false},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"1SvIyly7fm665flg"}
{"_id":"4kEqjcFxJqdDJYYc","name":"Spells","permission":{"default":0,"3zKQDMDqYUVrixL3":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>An astrologian casts astromancy spells which are drawn from the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/magic/spells-by-class/astrologian/\">astrologian spell list</a>. An astrologian begins play with 3 1st level astromancy spells of her choice. The astrologian also selects a number of additional 1st-level spells equal to her Wisdom modifier to add to her list of spells. Each time a character attains a new astrologian level, she gains two spells of her choice to add to her list of spells. The two free spells must be of spell levels she can cast. Like most mages, an astrologian can find or purchase scrolls with spells to add to her repertoire.</p>\n<p>To learn or cast a spell, the astrologian must have a Wisdom score equal to at least 10 + the spell level (Wis 11 for 1st-<wbr />level spells, Wis 12 for 2nd-<wbr />level spells, and so forth). The Difficulty Class for a saving throw against a astrologian&rsquo;s spell is 10 + the spell level + the astrologian&rsquo;s Wisdom modifier. In addition, an astrologian gains additional MP for having a high attribute (Wisdom&mdash;see&nbsp;Table: Bonus MP per Day (by Spell Level)&nbsp;on the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/system-rules/mp-system/\">MP System page</a>).</p>\n<p>Astrologians learn a number of cantrips, or 0-level spells. These spells are cast like any other spell, but they do not consume MP and may be used again. Astrologians begin with 4 0-level spells and gain an additional 0-level spell every three levels after 1st level.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Spells"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formulaicAttacks":{"count":{"formula":"","value":null},"bonus":{"formula":""},"label":null},"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":[],"dictionary":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Astrologian"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"nonlethal":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"conditionals":[],"identifiedName":"Spells"},"flags":{},"effects":[]}
{"name":"Fateful Touch (Su)","permission":{"default":0,"KvztsnF1yG9WE5bC":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 2nd level,&nbsp;<span lang=\"en-US\">the astrologian</span>&nbsp;can touch a creature as a standard action, granting them the ability to automatically roll a Natural 20 on one saving throw, skill check, or ability check. The automatic success must be used within one minute of being touched. The astrologian may use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + her Wisdom modifier.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Support"],["Rolls"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"standard"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":"10","units":"round"},"target":{"value":"One creature"},"range":{"value":null,"units":"touch","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":"none"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"day","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1","maxFormula":"3+@abilities.wis.mod"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formulaicAttacks":{"count":{"formula":"","value":null},"bonus":{"formula":""},"label":null},"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":[],"dictionary":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Astrologian"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"nonlethal":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","disabled":false},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"4vpL8dKCnoB9tZIX"}
{"name":"Forewarned (Su)","permission":{"default":0,"KvztsnF1yG9WE5bC":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 2nd level, the astrologian can always act in the surprise round even if she fails to make a Perception roll to notice a foe, but she is still considered flat-<wbr />footed until she takes an action. In addition, she receives a bonus on initiative checks equal to her Wisdom modifier. At 20th level, anytime she rolls initiative, assume the roll resulted in a natural 20.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Combat"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"special"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formulaicAttacks":{"count":{"formula":"","value":null},"bonus":{"formula":""},"label":null},"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[{"_id":"f0bub6ev","formula":"@abilities.wis.mod","operator":"add","target":"","subTarget":"init","modifier":"untyped","priority":0,"value":0}],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[{"text":"If the character is level 20, their initiative is [[@attributes.init.total + 20]] and the roll is considered a natural 20.","subTarget":"init"}],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom"