{"name":"The Heavens to Us (Su)","permission":{"default":0,"KvztsnF1yG9WE5bC":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 18th level, the astro<span lang=\"en-US\">logian</span>&nbsp;has honed her ability to call material from the stars.&nbsp;<span lang=\"en-US\">Sh</span>e can fill an area equal to a 60-ft.-diameter sphere with the void of space, which deals 10d6 points of&nbsp;<span lang=\"en-US\">ice</span>&nbsp;damage and immediately suffocates all creatures within the sphere, a Fortitude save (DC 10 + half of the astrologian&rsquo;s level + her Wisdom modifier) for half damage and staggered for 1 round rather than suffocated. She can use this ability a number of times per day equal to her Wisdom modifier.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Damage"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"standard"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":"@abilities.wis.mod","units":"round"},"target":{"value":"Area"},"range":{"value":"100","units":"ft","maxIncrements":"1","minValue":"","minUnits":"personal"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"day","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1","maxFormula":"@abilities.wis.mod"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"circle","size":"30","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formulaicAttacks":{"count":{"formula":"","value":null},"bonus":{"formula":""},"label":null},"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":"","damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":"10 + @abilities.wis.mod + floor(@classes.astrologian.lvl/2)","type":"fort","description":"Half Damage + Stagger"},"effectNotes":"All creatures within the sphere begin suffocating.  If they make the Fortitude save, they take half damage and become staggered instead.","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDex