{"name":"Insight (Su)","permission":{"default":0,"KvztsnF1yG9WE5bC":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 4th level, as an immediate action, the astrologian can immediately gain a bonus to her Reflex saving throws equal to her astrologian level. She can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + her Wisdom modifier.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Saving Throw"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"immediate"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":"Self"},"range":{"value":null,"units":"personal","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":"none"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"day","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1","maxFormula":"@abilities.wis.mod + 3"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formulaicAttacks":{"count":{"formula":"","value":null},"bonus":{"formula":""},"label":null},"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":[],"dictionary":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Astrologian"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"nonlethal":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","disabled":false},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"TmYAJ6pMfIsLRmsS"}
{"_id":"VlsyvYlFjjXZM42b","name":"Limit Break: Kinetic Card","permission":{"default":0,"3zKQDMDqYUVrixL3":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>This Limit Break allows the astrologian to fire a barrage of tarot cards in a 30-ft.-cone. Enemies within the area of effect take 2d6 points of non-elemental damage plus an additional 2d6 per four astrologian levels after 1st. A successful Reflex save (DC 10 + half of the astrologian&rsquo;s level + her Wisdom modifier) halves the damage. In addition, if enemies fail the saving throw, the tarot card explodes (no save), dealing 1d6 points of fire damage plus an additional 1d6 per four astrologian levels after 1st.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Limit Break"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"standard"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":"Enemies in 30-ft. cone"},"range":{"value":null,"units":"personal","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":"personal"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"day","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1","maxFormula":"@attributes.limitbreak.max"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"cone","size":"30","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[["2d6+(floor([[@classes.astrologian.lvl]]/4)*2)d6","non-elemental"]],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formulaicAttacks":{"count":{"formula":"","value":null},"bonus":{"formula":""},"label":null},"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":"","damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":"10 + (floor([[@classes.astrologian.lvl]]/2)) + @abilities.wis.mod","type":"ref","description":"Reflex half"},"effectNotes":"If Reflex save is failed, use Limit Break: Kinetic Card part 2 for secondary damage","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":[],"dictionary":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Astrologian"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"nonlethal":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"conditionals":[],"identifiedName":"Limit Break: Kinetic Card"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/clff20/icons/actions/LimitBreak.png","effects":[]}
{"name":"Royal Road (Su)","permission":{"default":0,"KvztsnF1yG9WE5bC":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 4th level, the astrologian&rsquo;s understanding of fortunetelling has grown considerably, allowing her to augment her tarot cards further. After she uses the Draw ability, she may use a free action to convert that card into an empowerment for a future reading. This empowerment affects the next card that the astrologian uses to empower an ally, from either the Draw ability or Spread ability.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>If the Balance or the Bole card is drawn, the effects are doubled.</li>\n<li>If the Arrow or the Shield card is drawn, the duration is doubled.</li>\n<li>If the Ewer or the Spire card is drawn, all allies within a 20-ft.-radius of the astrologian receive the effects</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Card"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"free"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":"One card the Astrologian has pulled."},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"","autoDeductCharges":false,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formulaicAttacks":{"count":{"formula":"","value":null},"bonus":{"formula":""},"label":null},"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"a