{"_id":"vPVTTxlOGioRpreg","name":"Astrology Secrets: Spray of Shooting Stars (Su)","permission":{"default":0,"KvztsnF1yG9WE5bC":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/astrologian/astrology-secrets/\">Astrology Secrets</a></p>\n<p>Spray of Shooting Stars (Su)</p>\n<p>As a standard action, the astrologian can unleash a ball of energy that explodes in a 5-foot radius burst dealing 1d4 points of fire damage per astrologian level. A successful Reflex save halves this damage. This attack has a range of 60 feet. She can fire one explosive ball per day, plus one additional ball per day at 5th level and for every 5 levels thereafter. She can fire more than one ball at a time, but creatures caught inside more than one simultaneous explosions only take damage once.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Astrology Secret"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"standard"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":"Area"},"range":{"value":"60","units":"ft","maxIncrements":"1","minValue":null,"minUnits":"melee"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"day","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1","maxFormula":"1+floor(@classes.astrologian.lvl/5)"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"circle","size":"5","overrideColor":true,"customColor":"#e4f32e","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[["(@classes.astrologian.lvl)d4","Fire"]],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formulaicAttacks":{"count":{"formula":"","value":null},"bonus":{"formula":""},"label":null},"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":"","damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":"0","type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":[],"dictionary":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Astrologian"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"nonlethal":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"conditionals":[],"identifiedName":"Astrology Secrets: Spray of Shooting Stars (Su)"},"flags":{},"effects":[]}
{"name":"Sect Powers: Serpent in the Sun (Su)","permission":{"default":0,"KvztsnF1yG9WE5bC":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/astrologian/sect-powers/\">Sect Powers</a></p>\n<p>Serpent in the Sun (Su)</p>\n<p>At 11th level, while under the Diurnal Sect, the astrologian no longer needs to eat to survive and she gains +2 bonus on saves against disease. In addition, at 14th level, she becomes immune to non-magical diseases and no longer need to drink water to survive. At 17th level, she becomes immune to magical diseases, gains a +2 bonus on saving throws against poisons, and only needs to sleep half as long to rest or recover from fatigue or exhaustion. At 20th level, she becomes immune to poison and fatigue. This ability only functions while the sun in shining.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Sect Power"],["Diurnal"],["Survival"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":null,"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formulaicAttacks":{"count":{"formula":"","value":null},"bonus":{"formula":""},"label":null},"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[{"text":"11th level: +2 vs disease, does not need to eat while in the sun.","subTarget":"allSavingThrows"},{"text":"14th level: Immune to non-magical diseases.  No longer requires water while in the sun.","subTarget":"allSavingThrows"},{"text":"17th level: Immune to magical diseases.  +2 to poisons while in the sun.","subTarget":"allSavingThrows"},{"text":"20th level: immune to poisons and fatigue while in the sun.","subTarget":"allSavingThrows"}],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":[],"dictionary":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Astrologian"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"nonlethal":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","disabled":false},"flags":{},"effects":[],"_id":"xAVP6tdZnGrhJt48"}
{"_id":"xb0IzTZY06AC0u55","name":"Draw (Su)","permission":{"default":0,"KvztsnF1yG9WE5bC":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Also at 1st level, an astrologian utilizes a special deck of tarot cards that float around her star globe. As a swift action, she may draw a card at random, rolling a 1d6 (see below). Once drawn, an astrologian may imbue the effects of the card on a single target within 30 feet. At 5th level and every four levels thereafter, the effects of the card increases by 1. The duration of the card&rsquo;s effect lasts a number of rounds equal to the astrologian&rsquo;s Wisdom modifier. The astrologian may use this ability a number of times per day equal to her astrologian level + her Wisdom modifier.</p>\n<h2 id=\"tablepress-14-name\">Astrologian: Draw</h2>\n<table id=\"tablepress-14\" style=\"width: 100%;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"5\" aria-labelledby=\"tablepress-14-name\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"width: 7%;\">d6</th>\n<th style=\"width: 25%;\">Tarot Card</th>\n<th style=\"width: 83.7524%;\">Benefit</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 5.44538%;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"width: 10.0285%;\">The Arrow (Su)</td>\n<td style=\"width: 83.7524%;\">This card grants the target a +1 luck bonus to attack rolls.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 5.44538%;\">2</td>\n<td style=\"width: 10.0285%;\">The Balance (Su)</td>\n<td style=\"width: 83.7524%;\">This card grants the target a +1 luck bonus to damage rolls. This extra damage is not multiplied on a critical hit.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 5.44538%;\">3</td>\n<td style=\"width: 10.0285%;\">The Bole (Su)</td>\n<td style=\"width: 83.7524%;\">This card provides a damage reduction of 1/- to the target.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 5.44538%;\">4</td>\n<td style=\"width: 10.0285%;\">The Ewer (Su)</td>\n<td style=\"width: 83.7524%;\">This card grants the target a +1 luck bonus on saving throws.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 5.44538%;\">5</td>\n<td style=\"width: 10.0285%;\">The Shield (Su)</td>\n<td style=\"width: 83.7524%;\">This card grants the target a +1 luck bonus to AC.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 5.44538%;\">6</td>\n<td style=\"width: 10.0285%;\">The Spire (Su)</td>\n<td style=\"width: 83.7524%;\">This card grants the target Fast Healing 2.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Support"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"swift"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":"@abilities.wis.mod","units":"round"},"target":{"value":"One target"},"range":{"value":"30","units":"ft","maxIncrements":"1","minValue":null,"minUnits":"personal"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"day","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1","maxFormula":"@classes.astrologian.lvl + @abilities.wis.mod"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formulaicAttacks":{"count":{"formula":"","value":null},"bonus":{"formula":""},"label":null},"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":"","damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":"","type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"The effect of the card is [[1d6]]","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":[],"dictionary":[]},"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Astrologian"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"nonlethal":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"conditionals":[],"identifiedName":"Draw (Su)"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/clff20/icons/FFxiv%20icons/FFXIVIcons%20Battle(PvE)/06_AST/draw.png","effects":[]}
{"_id":"y17KIyjTWHbZjk0y","name":"Astrology Secrets: Dweller in Darkness (Sp)","permission":{"default":0,"KvztsnF1yG9WE5bC":3},"type":"feat","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/astrologian/astrology-secrets/\">Astrology Secrets</a></p>\n<p>Dweller in Darkness (Sp)<span style=\"white-space: pre;\"> </span></p>\n<p>Prerequisite(s): Astrologian 11</p>\n<p>Once per day, the astrologan can cast her psyche into the void of space to attract the attention of a terrible otherworldly being. The dweller in darkness behaves in all ways as if she had cast <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/magic/spells/p/phantasmal-killer/\">phantasmal killer</a>. At 17th level, the dweller in darkness can be perceived by more than one creature, as if she had cast <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/magic/spells/w/weird/\">weird</a>.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Astrology Secret"]],"activation":{"cost":1,"type":"standard"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":""},"uses":{"value":0,"max":0,"per":"single","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formulaicAttacks":{"count":{"formula":"","value":null},"bonus":{"formula":""},"label":null},"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":0,"type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"lin